import { CommonModule } from '@angular/common'; import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { FormControl, FormGroup, ReactiveFormsModule, Validators } from '@angular/forms'; import { TranslateModule } from '@ngx-translate/core'; import {MatInputModule} from '@angular/material/input'; import {MatFormFieldModule} from '@angular/material/form-field'; @Component({ selector: 'app-contact-us', standalone: true, imports: [CommonModule, TranslateModule, ReactiveFormsModule, MatFormFieldModule, MatInputModule], templateUrl: './contact-us.component.html', styleUrl: './contact-us.component.scss' }) export class ContactUsComponent { public formGroup: FormGroup; constructor() { this.formGroup = new FormGroup({ name: new FormControl('', Validators.required), email: new FormControl('', Validators.required), phone: new FormControl('', Validators.required), message: new FormControl('', Validators.required), }) } }
